3480 REM CREATE AND BLINK Option 30 OBJECTS 100&101 FROM R12 P$3490 ROPEN 1003500 VISIBILITY 100,03510 CALL "RDRAW",P$,1,0,03520 RCLOSE 3530 ROPEN 1013540 VISIBILITY 101,03550 CALL "RDRAW",P$,1,0,03560 RCLOSE 3570 VISIBILITY 100,13580 BLINK 100,B0,B03590 VISIBILITY 101,13600 BLINK 101,B0,B03610 RETURN 3620 REM subroutine to DELETE blinking OBJECTS 100&1013630 BLINK 100,0,03640 VISIBILITY 100,03650 BLINK 101,0,03660 VISIBILITY 101,03670 DELETE 1003680 DELETE 1013690 RETURN 3700 REM subroutine to color T$ title text YELLOW3710 ROPEN 2003720 VISIBILITY 200,03730 PRINT T$3740 RCLOSE 3750 MOVE 5,1003760 ROPEN 2013770 VISIBILITY 201,03780 PRINT T$3790 RCLOSE 3800 VISIBILITY 200,13810 VISIBILITY 201,13820 MOVE 5,1003830 RETURN 3840 REM subroutine to DELETE YELLOW title text objects3850 VISIBILITY 200,03860 VISIBILITY 201,03870 RDELETE 2003880 RDELETE 2013890 RETURN 3900 REM subroutine create blinking ? at 0,1003910 MOVE 0,1003920 ROPEN 3003930 VISIBILITY 300,03940 BLINK 300,0.4,0.43950 PRINT "?"3960 MOVE 0,1003970 ROPEN 3013980 VISIBILITY 301,03990 BLINK 301,0.4,0.44000 PRINT "?"4010 RCLOSE 4020 RETURN4030 REM subroutine to enable VISIBLE ? at 0,1004040 VISIBILITY 300,14050 VISIBILITY 301,14060 RETURN4070 REM subroutine to disable VISIBLE ? at 0,1004080 VISIBILITY 300,04090 VISIBILITY 301,04100 RETURN